  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udc4b Hello! Welcome to *Waiyaki Tyre Services* \u2014 Limuru's fastest tyre help.\n\nI'm your booking assistant. Got a flat tyre or need tyre help? I'll get a mechanic to you quickly! \ud83d\udd27\n\nWhat service do you need today?",
  "name": "booking_bot"
